verses.verse: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%> <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3068>LORD<s%> from the <S%H8064>heavens:<s%> <S%H1984>praise<s%> him in the <S%H4791>heights.<s%>

<S%H1984>Praise<s%> you him, <S%H8121>sun<s%> and <S%H3394>moon:<s%> <S%H1984>praise<s%> him, <S%H3605>all<s%> you <S%H3556>stars<s%> of <S%H216>light.<s%>
<S%H1984>Praise<s%> him, you <S%H8064>heavens<s%> of <S%H8064>heavens,<s%> and you <S%H4325>waters<s%> that be <S%H4791>above<s%> the <S%H8064>heavens.<s%>
Let them <S%H1984>praise<s%> the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD:<s%> for he <S%H6680>commanded,<s%> and they were <S%H1254>created.<s%>
He has also <S%H5975>established<s%> them for <S%H5703>ever<s%> and <S%H5769>ever:<s%> he has <S%H5414>made<s%> a <S%H2706>decree<s%> which shall not <S%H5674>pass.<s%>
<S%H4428>Kings<s%> of the <S%H776>earth,<s%> and <S%H3605>all<s%> <S%H3816>people;<s%> <S%H8269>princes,<s%> and <S%H3605>all<s%> <S%H8199>judges<s%> of the <S%H776>earth:<s%>

Let them <S%H1984>praise<s%> the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>LORD:<s%> for his <S%H8034>name<s%> <S%H905>alone<s%> is <S%H7682>excellent;<s%> his <S%H1935>glory<s%> is <S%H4791>above<s%> the <S%H776>earth<s%> and <S%H8064>heaven.<s%>

He also <S%H7311>exalts<s%> the <S%H7161>horn<s%> of his <S%H5971>people,<s%> the <S%H8416>praise<s%> of <S%H3605>all<s%> his <S%H2623>saints;<s%> even of the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel,<s%> a <S%H5971>people<s%> <S%H7138>near<s%> to him. <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3050>LORD.<s%>
